Package: ecoPointXAI
Type: Package
Title: Explainable 3D Forest Analytics with PointNet and LiDAR
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Muhammad", "Qasim", email = "khanjiqasim@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a full pipeline for explainable 3D forest analysis 
    using voxelized LiDAR data and PointNet neural networks. 
    Includes preprocessing, feature engineering, training, explainability, 
    and visualization modules for ecological interpretation.
